'''塞德里克·里卡多·阿尔维斯·苏亚雷斯'''（'''Cédric Ricardo Alves Soares''' {{small|{{link-en|Order of Merit (Portugal)|Order of Merit (Portugal)|ComM}}}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://anibalcavacosilva.arquivo.presidencia.pt/?idc=10&idi=56611&action=7|title=Presidente Cavaco Silva condecorou selecção nacional de futebol sub-20|trans_title=President Cavaco Silva decorated national under-20 football team|publisher=Arquivo Presidência|language=pt|date=2011-09-06|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116181041/https://anibalcavacosilva.arquivo.presidencia.pt/?idc=10&idi=56611&action=7}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/euro_2016/artigo/2016/07/10/euro2016-marcelo-condecora-jogadores-com-grau-de-comendador-da-ordem-do-merito|title=Marcelo condecora jogadores com Grau de Comendador da Ordem do Mérito|trans_title=Marcelo decorates players with ''Grau de Comendador da Ordem do Mérito''|publisher=SAPO|language=pt|date=2016-07-10|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220124058/http://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/euro_2016/artigo/2016/07/10/euro2016-marcelo-condecora-jogadores-com-grau-de-comendador-da-ordem-do-merito}}</ref>，{{bd|1991年|8月31日|||catIdx=S}}），是一名[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]的職業足球運動員，出生于[[德国|德國]]。現時效力[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英格兰足球超级联赛]]球隊[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿森纳]]。司職[[右後衛|右後衛]]。

== 球會生涯 ==
=== 阿仙奴 ===
2020年1月31日，薛迪被外借至[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英格兰足球超级联赛]]球隊[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿森纳]]，為期6個月<ref>{{cite web |title=Arsenal sign defender Cedric Soares from Southampton on loan |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51326032 |website=BBC Sport |accessdate=2020-01-31 |language=en |date=2020-01-31 |archive-date=2020-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201210403/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51326032 }}</ref>。6月24日，球會宣佈他於合約結束後，自由轉會至阿仙奴<ref>{{cite web |title=Four players extend stay at club |url=https://www.arsenal.com/news/four-players-extend-stay-club |publisher=Arsenal F.C. |accessdate=2020-06-24 |date=2020-06-24 |language=en |archive-date=2020-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907030126/https://www.arsenal.com/news/four-players-extend-stay-club |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年7月1日，薛迪於主勝[[諾域治足球會|諾域治]]4比0的聯賽比賽中首次代表阿仙奴上陣，他於第77分鐘後備入替，並在4分鐘後於20碼外射入1球<ref>{{cite web |last1=Johnston |first1=Neil |title=Arsenal 4 Norwich City 0 |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/52072989 |website=BBC Sport |accessdate=2020-07-01 |language=en |date=2020-07-01 |archive-date=2020-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009003050/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/52072989 }}</ref>。2020年8月29日，薛迪於[[英格蘭社區盾|英格蘭社區盾]]對陣[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]的比賽中後備上陣，他於[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]階段射入第3個十二碼，助球隊以5比4擊敗對手<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thefa.com/news/2020/aug/29/arsenal-liverpool-mens-fa-community-shield-match-report-290820 |title=ARSENAL BEAT LIVERPOOL 5–4 ON PENALTIES TO WIN THE FA COMMUNITY SHIELD |publisher=The Football Association |date=2020-08-29 |language=en |accessdate=2020-08-30 |archive-date=2020-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831035916/https://www.thefa.com/news/2020/aug/29/arsenal-liverpool-mens-fa-community-shield-match-report-290820 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

